	   <tr><td colspan=2>They receive 1 handed blunt, 2 handed blunt, piercing (both 1 handed and 2 handed), and hand to hand.&nbsp;&nbsp;The cap is 200 at level 50 for all these skills, but the cap at 60 is 250 for hand to hand and only 225 for the other weapon skills.  This is why you see most beastlords using H2H weapons.<br><br>As for extra skills, we get kick at level 5, dodge at 10, dual wield at 17, block at 25, and riposte at 40.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Mar  1 11:17:40 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>[55 Preserver] Senlarr (Wood Elf)<br>[53 Pathfinder] Maeras (Half Elf)<br>[51 Disciple] Seniten (Human)<br>Mithaniel Marr</td></tr>
